ange report to group -5163901258:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 15p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 1:49 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 13:49 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776261025125,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"0a29334a\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the stored state in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_8f4fqu2shvyq_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"activeMinutes\": 60,\n                \"messageLimit\": 2\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_8f4fqu2shvyq_2\",\n              \"name\": \"memory_search\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"query\": \"heartbeat state DTLX 15p report\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 450,\n            \"output\": 98,\n            \"totalTokens\": 15274,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14726