"runtimeMs\": 493818,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:52f0c795-a0e6-4fbc-9372-fe4cf966a590\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/267be008-a295-4e44-aab6-59f510cf7591.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The branch was pushed successfully. Now let me summarize what was done and what the user needs to do next.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**✅ Done! Branch `feat/complete-setup` đã push lên GitHub.**\\n\\n### Tóm tắt những gì đã fix và đẩy lên:\\n\\n| File | Fix |\\n|------|-----|\\n| `bin/ahv-setup.js` | ✅ `applyCredentials` set đủ 3 trường Confluence (`CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_USERNAME`, `CONF_TOKEN`) |\\n| `configs/team-*.json` | ✅ Fix `CONFLUENCE_*` → `CONF_*` (đúng env var names) |\\n| `bin/ahv-setup.js` | ✅ Skills unpack đúng path (`~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`) |\\n| `bin/ahv-setup.js` | ✅ Copy agent files từ `agent-defs/` trong setup repo |\\n| `install.sh` | ✅ Pipe mode: tự detect non-TTY → `--yes` → không treo |\\n| `skills.pack` | ✅ Restore đúng key `ahv-openclaw-2026` (bị hỏng ở commit cũ) |\\n\\n### Bước tiếp theo cho Lead:\\n```\\n🌐 GitHub: https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/pull/new/feat/complete-setup\\n→ Tạo Pull Request: feat/complete-setup → main\\n→ Review & Merge\\n```\\n\\nSau khi merge, user mới chạy setup sẽ hoạt động đầy đủ — credentials apply đúng, skills unpack đúng, agents copy đúng.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 278,\n            \"output\": 36