e: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 1:49 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 13:49 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776261025125,"__openclaw":{"id":"0a29334a","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the stored state in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8f4fqu2shvyq_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"activeMinutes":60,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8f4fqu2shvyq_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat state DTLX 15p report"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":450,"output":98,"totalTokens":15274,"cacheRead":14726,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776261025150,"responseId":"062ecaa1b05451804076f0c415e18073","__openclaw":{"id":"6caf0a69","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","kind":"group","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"webchat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-5163901258","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776260837704,"sessionId":"9d41c813-4b84-4cc7-aab2-4c3b88fb4bc1","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34419,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776260574407,"endedAt":1776260583206,"runtimeMs":8799,"childSessions":["agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e-8c76-42e7-ac2a-f1474568e0d4","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:469f1534-e128-44ea-af0d-73710c607372","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:sub